(1,	'Miss Barbara Lubaczewska our new Principal',	'activities/November2022/ylhGaVSP5hmsfYnI6f6k.jpg',	'<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: #434549; font-family: ArticulatCF-Normal; font-size: 17px; background-color: #ffffff;\">We are delighted to announce the appointment of Miss Barbara&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">Lubaczewska as the Principal of the English International School Baghdad.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: #434549; font-family: ArticulatCF-Normal; font-size: 17px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Barbara has over 30 years in British education, having held&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">international and UK Headship positions since 2007. She holds a&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">Bachelor of Arts (BA) in education from the University of East&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">Anglia, UK, and she has enjoyed consultancy work in the areas of&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">school improvement, inspection, safeguarding, and leadership.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: #434549; font-family: ArticulatCF-Normal; font-size: 17px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Barbara is also an Associate Leadership Trainer of Karen Ardley&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">Associates, UK, and has travelled the world facilitating leadership&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">programmes to aspiring leaders. Barbara strongly believes in&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">distributed leadership and empowering young teachers to&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">engage effectively in middle leadership roles. Her work as a&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">Counsellor for ChildLine UK and as a Safeguarding lead has&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">helped to shape her work on establishing and embedding Values&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">programmes in schools. She has also worked closely with UK&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">universities as a mentor of PGCE students and is excited to&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">continue this work in school, being a firm believer in supporting&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">student teachers to be aspirational and brave in their approach&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">to teaching.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: #434549; font-family: ArticulatCF-Normal; font-size: 17px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Barbara has worked extensively in the Middle East and Europe&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">and opened schools in London, Prague, Amsterdam, Dubai, and&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">Abu Dhabi. Barbara&rsquo;s passion for school improvement ensures&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">that her key priority is continually establishing high-performing&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">teams and promoting each student&rsquo;s academic success and well-being.</span></p>',	'2022-11-04 22:16:28',	'2022-11-04 22:16:28',	NULL,	NULL,	NULL),
(2,	'School Registration is now open!',	'activities/November2022/UWpAoQ5nqRYsC6Fhf0Uh.png',	'<div class=\"post-content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #434549; position: relative; font-family: ArticulatCF-Normal; font-size: 17px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px;\">Registration for the new academic year has opened. School seats are limited. If you wish to register your child, you can fill out the&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: none; transition-property: color, background-color, border-color; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear;\" href=\"https://eis.edu.iq/online-registration\">registration form</a>&nbsp;online and a member of the registration team will contact you.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"fusion-sharing-box fusion-theme-sharing-box fusion-single-sharing-box\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; justify-content: space-between; margin-top: 60px; --sharing_box_tagline_text_color: var(--awb-color7); --sharing_social_links_font_size: 20px; display: flex; min-height: 70px; width: 1860px; align-items: center; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; color: #434549; font-family: ArticulatCF-Normal; font-size: 17px; padding: var(--h4_typography-margin-top,0) 0px var(--h4_typography-margin-bottom,0) 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>',	'2022-11-04 22:17:39',	'2022-11-04 22:17:39',	NULL,	NULL,	NULL),
(3,	'Dr. Falah Sharad is our new doctor',	'activities/November2022/aHDjb4ItDObXiVdXdupq.png',	'<div class=\"cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql o9v6fnle ii04i59q\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #434549; font-family: ArticulatCF-Normal; font-size: 17px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Mental health is an ongoing concern for many parents and teachers, at the English International School Baghdad we ensure that we address every aspect in our students&rsquo; lives, and we want to make sure we have mentally as well as physically healthy children. The mental and physical wellbeing of our students is our priority. Being mentally healthy during childhood means reaching developmental and emotional milestones and learning healthy social skills and how to cope with problems in life. Mentally healthy children have a positive quality of life and can function well at home, in school, and in their communities.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql o9v6fnle ii04i59q\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #434549; font-family: ArticulatCF-Normal; font-size: 17px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">We are glad to share that Dr. Falah Sharad is our new doctor, he is a consultant family physician FRACGP with subspeciality in paediatric psychology, a fellow of the royal Australian college of general practitioners FRACGP &ndash; 2003, a consultant family physician (with subspecialty in mental health diseases especially for children) for 19 years in Australia. Welcome Dr. Sharad!</div>\r\n</div>',	'2022-11-04 22:18:50',	'2022-11-04 22:18:50',	NULL,	NULL,	NULL),
