(74,	'Math end of term 1 material',	1,	'<p style=\"margin: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">Dear grade 4,</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\">Your material for the end of term 1 is going to be as the following:</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><strong>1-Multiplication:</strong></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\"><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">(1-12) timetable</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\"><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">Multiplying by 1-Digit.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\"><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">Multiplying by 10 multiples.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><strong>2-Division:</strong></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\"><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">Long division.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\"><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">Dividing by 1-Digit only.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\"><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">Adding and Subtracting up to 4-Digits.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: