(161,	'Research your country',	10,	'<p>Make notes about the geography and culture of your country.</p>\r\n<p>Every student has chosen a country now. Go on the internet and find out about the geography and culture of your country, to prepare for your project.</p>\r\n<p>Geography - Find out</p>\r\n<p>- Which continent</p>\r\n<p>- Seas and rivers</p>\r\n<p>- Population</p>\r\n<p>- Capital city</p>\r\n<p>- Landscape</p>\r\n<p>- Size</p>\r\n<p>- Climate</p>\r\n<p>Culture - Find out about</p>\r\n<p>- Famous buildings</p>\r\n<p>- Places to visit</p>\r\n<p>- Famous people from history</p>\r\n<p>- Traditional foods</p>\r\n<p>- Traditional games and activities</p>\r\n<p>- Traditional clothes</p>\r\n<p>- Leader</p>\r\n<p>- Wars</p>\r\n<p>Make notes. This is for your assessment that will make up your end of term grade for IMYC.</p>',	'2022-12-04 09:46:27',	'2022-12-04 09:46:27',	NULL,	495,	1),
