(197,	'Exam Topics Grade 1 B',	1,	'<p><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Dear parents,</span><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\">I hope you are all doing well.&nbsp;❤️</span><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;The winter exams are nearly here and our revision week will commence this coming Sunday.</span><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\">I encourage you all to revise the topics with your children at home that we will be studying for the exams.</span><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\">I have attached a Review Sheet with practice questions for the exams and information to revise.</span><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Please feel free to practice a few of the questions daily with your children. I will be also revising in the classroom so they will be prepared and feel comfortable to sit the exams.</span><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\">I really don\'t want the children to feel stressed or anxious about the exams so honestly once they are really trying their best then that\'s the most important thing that matters. They are making amazing progress and they are so eager to learn and always curious.&nbsp;</span><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\">I wish you all the best and do not hesitate to contact me in relation to the Review Sheet.</span><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Kind regards,</span><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Ms. Fay</span><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\" /><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\">G1B</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><u><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"font-size: 13.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Review sheet for Grade 1 exams.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></u></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><u><span lang=\"EN\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">&nbsp;</span></span></u></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\">&nbsp;</span></em></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\">&nbsp;</span></em></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\">&nbsp;</span></em></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\">&nbsp;</span></em></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\">&nbsp;</span></em></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\">Dear parents,</span></em></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN\">&nbsp;</span></em></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span lang=\"EN\">Our lovely students have been working very hard and I am so proud of them.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span lang=\"EN\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong style=\"ms