(210,	'الأفعال الخمسة',	2,	'<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-7a97053e-7fff-923f-d25c-fa191a04ed40\" dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffff00; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">الأفعال الخمسة&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">هو كل فعل مضارع اتصل به ألف الإثنين أو واو الجماعة أو ياء المخاطبة&nbsp; ويكون على خمسة صيغة&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">الفعل (درس)&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; color: #ff0000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">يدرسون / تدرسون&nbsp; / يدرسان / تدرسان&nbsp; / تدرسين</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">🌹 </span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffff00; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">تعرب الأفعال الخمسة إذا كانت مرفوعة </span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">(فعل مضارع مرفوع وعلامة رفعه ثبوت النون لأنه من الأفعال الخمسة)&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">الطلاب </span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; color: #ff0000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">يكتبون</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> الدرسَ</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; color: #ff0000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">يكتبون:</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> فعل مضارع مرفوع وعلامة رفعه ثبوت النون لأنه من الأفعال الخمسة</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">والواو ضمير متصل مبني في محل رفع فاعل&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffff00; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">🌹 تعرب الأفعال الخمسة إذا كانت منصوبة</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> أي قبلها أداة نصب&nbsp; (فعل مضارع منصوب وعلامة نصبه حذف&nbsp; النون لأنه من الأفعال الخمسة)&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\"