n: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">الضمائر (تاء الفاعل ، نا المتكلمين ، نون النسوة ) جميعهن يعربن ضمير متصل مبني في محل رفع فاعل&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; color: #ff0000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">٣- الضم : 👈🏻 إذا اتصل به واو الجماعة</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffff00; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">مثل</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> درسُوا ، لعبُوا ، نجحُوا&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">يكون الإعراب 👈🏻 فعل ماضٍ مبني على الضم&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><br style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto;\" /><br style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto;\" /></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; color: #ff0000; background-color: #ffff00; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">فعل الأمر : </span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">هو حدوث شيء بعد زمن التكلم وهو مبني دائمًا&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">علامة بناء فعل الأمر&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; color: #ff0000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">١- السكون 👈🏻 إذا لم يتصل به شيء</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> مثل ادرسْ ، العبْ ، ارسمْ ، اكتبْ</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: