ont-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> المجتهدين&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">لن👈🏻 حرف نصب&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">يفشلوا 👈🏻 فعل مضارع منصوب وعلامة نصبه حذف النون لأنه من الأفعال الخمسة&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">والواو ضمير متصل في محل رفع فاعل&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #00ffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">اجتهدي </span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; color: #ff0000; background-color: #00ffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">كي تنجحي</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #00ffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">كي 👈🏻 حرف نصب&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">تنجحي 👈🏻 فعل مضارع منصوب وعلامة نصبه حذف النون لأنه من الأفعال الخمسة&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">والياء ضمير متصل في محل رفع فاعل&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #00ffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">اكتبَا </span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; color: #ff0000; background-color: #00ffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">كي تنالَا</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #00ffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> رضى المدرس</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">كي 👈🏻 حرف نصب</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">تنالا👈🏻 فعل مضارع منصوب وعلامة نصبه حذف النون لأنه من الأفعال الخمسة&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">والألف ضمير متصل في محل رفع فاعل</span></p>\r\n<p><br style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto;\" /><br style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto;\" /></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; color: #ff0000; background-color: #ffff00; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">جزم الفعل المضارع</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">يجزم الفعل المضارع إذا جاء قبله أحد أدوات الجزم وأدوات الجزم ( لم - لمّا - لام الأمر - لا الناهية)&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; color: #ff0000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">لم</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> 👈🏻 مثل 👈🏻 </span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; color: #ff0000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">لم ينجحْ</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> المهملُ&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; color: #ff0000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">لمَّا</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp; (تكون بمعنى لم)👈🏻 مثل 👈🏻 جلستُ بعيدًا </span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; color: #ff0000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ولمَّا أنظرْ</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> شيئًا .&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; color: #ff0000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">لام الأمر</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> (تدل على الطلب) 👈🏻 مثل 👈🏻 </span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; color: #ff0000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">لِتسمعْ</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> كلامي جيدًا&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; color: #ff0000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">لا الناهية </span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">( كذلك تدل على الطلب) 👈🏻 مثل 👈🏻</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; color: #ff0000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> لا تكذبْ</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> / &nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; color: #ff0000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">لا تهملْ</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> واجبك&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; color: #ff0000; background-color: #ffff00; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">علامات جزم الفعل المضارع&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffff00; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">١- يجزم الفعل المضارع وعلامة جزمه السكون إذا كان صحيح الآخر</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: 