(260,	'IPC project for exams',	5,	'<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: normal;\"><strong><u><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Comic Sans MS\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">IPC</span></u></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Comic Sans MS\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Comic Sans MS\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">For IPC we will create a poster at school.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Comic Sans MS\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Comic Sans MS\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">You will create a poster (in class) but you may prepare for poster by knowing the following information (you don\'t need to memorise the information and you can write it down as notes to use when we are completing the posters):</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Comic Sans MS\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Comic Sans MS\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">1. What is a volcano?</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Comic Sans MS\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">2. Where are volcanoes located?</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Comic Sans MS\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">3. An interesting fact (from our worksheets that we did on volcanoes)</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Comic Sans MS\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">4. What is the effect of a volcano?</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Comic Sans MS\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">5. What are dormant, active and extinct volcanoes?</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Comic Sans MS\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">6. How to label a volcano</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-he