tyle=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #00ff00; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">١- مفرد /</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> الحال المفرد&nbsp; وهو عبارة عن كلمة واحدة ونقول نوع الحال مفرد حتى وإن كان مثنى أو جمع وتكون إجابة عن السؤال كيف&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">مثل وصل العمال </span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffff00; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">متأخرينَ</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">وقفت الفتيات </span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffff00; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">منتبهاتٍ</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">وجدنا اللص </span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffff00; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">خائفًا</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #00ff00; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">٢- الجملة /</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> والجملة تكون على نوعين أما جملة اسمية أو جملة فعلية&nbsp; والحال اذا كان جملة لا يعرف من خلال المعنى وإنما يعرف من خلال قادة الجمل وأشباه الجمل بعد المعارف أحوال&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">مثل/ وصل أحمد </span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffff00; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">يبتسم</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; color: #ff0000; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">يبتسم 👈🏻</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> فعل مضارع مرفوع وعلامة رفعه الضمة الظاهرة على آخره والفاعل ضمير مستتر والجملة الفعلية في محل نصب حال&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; color: #ff0000; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">معلومة 👈🏻 قلنا الجملة الفعلية في محل نصب حال لأن قبل الجملة الفعلية اسم معرفة (أحمد)&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">مثال/ شاهدتُ العصافيرَ </span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffff00; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">تطيرُ</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; color: #ff0000; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">تطيرُ / </span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">فعل مضارع مرفوع وعلامة رفعه الضمة الظاهرة على آخره والفاعل ضمير مستتر والجملة الفعلية في محل نصب حال&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; color: #ff0000; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">معلومة 👈🏻 قلنا الجملة الفعلية في محل نصب حال لأن قبل الجملة الفعلية اسم معرفة (العصافير)&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #00ff00; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">٣- شبه الجملة / </span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">شبه الجملة هي التي تتكون من حرف جر واسم مجرور أو من ظرف ومضاف إليه&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; color: #ff0000; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">حروف الجر 👈🏻من ، في ، عن ، على ، إلى ، الباء ، الكاف ، اللام&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">مثل شاهدت السيارة </span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffff00; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">في المعرض</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">في حرف جر والمعرض اسم مجرور وعلامة جره الكسرة وشبه الجملة في محل نصب حال&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">وقفت الفراشة </span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffff00; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">بين الشجر&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">بين 👈🏻 ظرف مكان منصوب / الشجر👈🏻 مضاف إليه مجرور وشبه الجملة في محل نصب حال&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">وقف المعلم </span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffff00; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">أمام التلاميذ&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">أمام 👈🏻 ظرف مكان منصوب / التلاميذ 👈🏻 مضاف إليه مجرور&nbsp; وشبه الجملة في محل نصب حال&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; color: #ff0000; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">معلومة / كل شبه جملة قبلها اسم معرفة ستعرب في محل نصب حال&nbsp;</span></p>',	'2023-01-08 09:46:51',	'2023-01-08 09:46:51',	NULL,	497,	1),
