(278,	'English Homework - January 8, 2023',	3,	'<p>Hello!</p>\r\n<p>My name is Miss Zoe and I am 4A Homeroom Teacher.</p>\r\n<p>Today\'s homework:</p>\r\n<p>1. Finish page 80 in iPrimary English Activity book (blue book).</p>\r\n<p>2. Read the first 20 pages of \"Two Left Feet\" in iPrimary Fiction Anthology (white book).&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Thank you!</p>',	'2023-01-08 12:35:38',	'2023-01-08 12:35:38',	NULL,	521,	1),
