(330,	'Homework: Video Response',	3,	'<p>Steps to a Video Response:</p>\r\n<p>1.) Watch the attached video <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">OR</span> you may choose a video/podcast (in English) that interests you. Any video/podcast you choose should be at least 6 minutes long. Be sure to write the title and the name of the person/company that produced it.</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Benefits of a Good Night\'s Sleep\" href=\"https://youtu.be/gedoSfZvBgE\">Link to Video</a></p>\r\n<p>2.) Write <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">one paragraph</span> <strong>summarizing </strong>the main points of the video.</p>\r\n<p>3.) Write a <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">second paragraph</span> <strong>responding </strong>to the video (Examples of information that can go in this response: Do you agree/disagree? Was there any surprising information? Does this apply your life? Did it change the way you think/feel about something? What drew you to this video?)</p>\r\n<p>4.) Identify at least 3 terms you came across in the video that you were unfamiliar with and give a definition in your own words.</p>',	'2023-01-17 09:59:00',	'2023-01-17 10:09:38',	NULL,	525,	1),
