(342,	'Self-Sustainable house',	5,	'<p>The students should draw a self sustainable house. This should include but is not limited to water, food, shelter and all any other neccesities they decide they need. It should show the location (i.e.. by a river, on the beach, in the moutains. The students can look on the internet for ideas but should not draw a picture from the interent. They need to use their own imagination and creativity. Markers don\'t look good on paper; so please use colored pencils. The pictures will probably be posted on the board, so please have the students do their best. I realize that some of the parents are excllent artists, but it should be the students work. However, parents are allowed to help but not do it.</p>',	'2023-01-17 12:48:19',	'2023-01-17 12:48:19',	NULL,	520,	1);
