(344,	'No Red Ink',	3,	'<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #76838f; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\">This is my third day listing this. Please Register for No Red Ink. Then take the assigned diagnostic. This test will help to determine the areas that need the most improvement. It is vital that the students complete the diagnostic without help. It is difficult but it is designed to find out their strengths and weeknesses.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin: 0px; color: #76838f; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Please read the instructions carefully when registering.&nbsp; Please click this link and follow the instructions carefully. <a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; background-color: transparent; color: #337ab7; text-decoration-line: none;\" title=\"Register for No Red Ink\" href=\"https://www.noredink.com/join/goofy-sparrow-87\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Register for No Red Ink</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin: 0px; color: #76838f; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin: 0px; color: #76838f; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; background-color: transparent; color: #337ab7; text-decoration-line: none;\" title=\"No Red Ink Registration\" href=\"https://www.noredink.com/join/goofy-sparrow-87\">Class Code: goofy sparrow 87</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin: 0px; color: #76838f; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin: 0px; color: #76838f; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-se