(345,	'Spelling quiz',	3,	'<p>Dear Parents,</p>\r\n<p>It seems I\'ve contracted the cold going around n am unable to make to school. Very sorry. We will still have our spelling quiz on Thursday from the words found on pages 94, 98 n 106. I will miss tomorrow but hopefully be better by Thursday</p>',	'2023-01-17 14:03:21',	'2023-01-17 14:03:21',	NULL,	523,	1),
(346,	'Spelling Quiz',	3,	'<p>Dear Parents,</p>\r\n<p>Apparently I\'ve contracted the cold going around. It has wiped me out. I will miss tomorrow but hopefully better by Thursday. We will have our spelling quiz as planned from pages 94, 98 n 106 found at the bottom. Very sorry about my absence.</p>',	'2023-01-17 14:05:29',	'2023-01-17 14:05:29',	NULL,	523,	1),
(347,	'Reading',	3,	'<p>Students should choose a book of interest and read every day at least 30 minutes to hopefully improve their reading but to also encourage enjoyment of reading. Im trying in the near future to have them record their reading once a week..just 2 min sample. I will find an appropriate media to do this and contact you.</p>',	'2023-01-17 14:07:52',	'2023-01-17 14:07:52',	NULL,	523,	1),
(348,	'Reading',	3,	'<p>Students should choose an interesting reading book or extraxt they like. I would like them to read 30 minutes every day if possible to improve their reading but also to encourage enjoyment of reading. I plan to have them record a 2 minute sample once a week n send to me but I need to find an acceptable media to do so. I will contact you when I have one.</p>',	'2023-01-17 14:10:35',	'2023-01-17 14:10:35',	NULL,	523,	1),
