(351,	'الاسماء الخمسة',	2,	'<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffff00; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">يجب كتابته في الدفتر وحل تمريناته في الدفتر </span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-733d16d0-7fff-d903-9211-86334da2dd21\" dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffff00; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">الأسماء الخمسة&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; color: #ff0000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">هي خمسة أسماء (أبٌ ، أخٌ ، حمٌ، فو ، ذو)&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffff00; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ملحوظة🤗🤗</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">تعرب الأسماء الخمسة حسب موقعها من الجملة و تعرب بالحروف 🤔🤔 ( الواو رفعا - بالألف نصبًا&nbsp; - وبالياء جرًّا )&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">جاء أبوك&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">أبوك 👈🏻 فاعل مرفوع وعلامة رفعه الواو لأنه من الأسماء الخمسة&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">رأيتُ أخاك&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">أخاك 👈🏻 مفعول به منصوب وعلامة نصبه الألف لأنه من الأسماء الخمسة&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">سلمتُ على حميكِ&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">حميكِ👈🏻 اسم مجرور وعلامة جره الياء لأنه من الأسماء الخمسة&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffff00; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">أمثلة</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">وصل ذو الخلق / رأيت ذا المال يتصدق / أحسن إلى ذي الأدب&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">فوك نظيفٌ جدا &nbsp; /.&nbsp; &nbsp; إنَّ فاك صغيرٌ &nbsp; &nbsp; / ضع الطعام في فيها&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">🥰 ذو معناها صاحب&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">🥰 فو معناها فم&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; color: #ff0000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">لكي تعرب الأسماء الخمسة بالحروف يجب أن تتوفر فيها بعض الشروط&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; color: #ff0000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">١</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; color: #ff0000; background-color: #00ff00; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">-</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #00ff00; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> أن تكون هذه الأسماء مفردة مثلا (أبو - أخو حمو&hellip;&hellip;)&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">وإذا كانت هذه الإسماء مثنى ستعربُ بإعراب المثنى (الألف في حالة الرفع والياء في حالتي النصب والجر)&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">مثلا جاء الأبوان&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">الأبوان 👈🏻 فاعل مرفوع وعلامة رفعه الألف لأنه مثنى&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">رأيت الأبوين&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">الأبوين 👈🏻 مفعول به منصوب وعلامة نصبه الياء لأنه مثنى&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">وإذا كانت جمع فإنها ستعربُ بالحروف (الضمة رفعا ، والفتحة نصبا ، الكسرة جرا)&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">جاء الأباءُ</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">الأباءُ 👈🏻 فاعل مرفوع وعلامة رفعه الضمة&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">رأيتُ الآباءَ&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">الآباءَ👈🏻 مفعول به منصوب وعلامة نصبه الفتحة&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; color: #ff0000; background-color: #00ff00; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">٢-</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #00ff00; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> أن تكون هذه الأسماء مضافة إلى اسم ظاهر&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">مثلا جاء أبو محمدٍ&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ابو👈🏻 فاعل مرفوع وعلامة رفعه الواو لأنه من الأسماء الخمسة وهو مضاف&nbsp; ومحمد مضاف إليه مجرور وعلامة جره الكسرة.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #00ff00; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">أو مضافة إلى ضمير عدا ياء المتكلم&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">مثلا جاء أخو</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; color: #ff0000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ك</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">أخوك 👈🏻 فاعل مرفوع وعلامة رفعه الواو لأنه من الأسماء الخمسة وهو مضاف والكاف ضمير متصل في محل جر مضاف إليه&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffff00; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ملحوظة🤗</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> إذا أضيفت هذه الأسماء الخمسة إلى ياء المتكلم ستُعرب بالحركات المقدرة&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.38; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-w