(372,	'Doubling and Halving',	1,	'<p>Hello 2A,</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Since some of us are still struggling&nbsp; with doubling and halving, please watch this video to help you to understand how to double and halve numbers.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"doubling and halving\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hclv1hUEsoY\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hclv1hUEsoY</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you would more practice, please try to these at home if you like:)</p>\r\n<p>Use the same method as in the video.</p>\r\n<p>1. Double 67</p>\r\n<p>2. Double 88</p>\r\n<p>3. Double 94</p>\r\n<p>4. Double 85</p>\r\n<p>5. Double 74</p>\r\n<p>6. Half of 25</p>\r\n<p>7. Half of 68</p>\r\n<p>8. Half of 89</p>\r\n<p>9. Half of 34</p>\r\n<p>10. Half of 88</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>I hope this helps and please remember that we will write a quiz on doubling and halving on Sunday.</p>\r\n<p>See you on Sunday!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',	'2023-01-19 15:40:00',	'2023-01-19 15:41:09',	NULL,	482,	1),
