(369,	'Winter Sweaters / بلوزات شتائية',	'Dear parents,\r\n\r\nWe are selling EISB winter sweaters for our students. If you are interested buying them, please send $30 with your child ASAP as they are very limited.\r\n\r\nKindly go to \"activities\" to view the sweater. \r\n\r\nRegards, \r\n\r\nاولياء الامور الاعزاء،\r\n\r\nلقد قمنا بتوفير بلوزات شتائية خاصة بالمدرسة الانكليزية الدولية لطلبتنا.اذا كنتم ترغبون بالشراء، الرجاء ارسال مبلغ 30 دولار مع طفلكم بأسرع وقت وذلك لكون الكمية محدوة جدا.\r\n\r\nالرجاء النقر على \"انشطة\" للاطلاع على شكل البلوز.\r\n\r\nمع اطيب التحيات',	0,	'2023-01-08 09:16:34',	'2023-01-08 09:16:34',	NULL),
(370,	'Weekly Lesson Objectives',	'Dear parents,\r\n\r\nWe would like to inform you that effective Sunday, the 15th of January we will be sharing \'weekly lesson objectives\' with you in order to be aware what your child is learning.\r\n\r\nRegards, \r\n\r\nاولياء الامور الاعزاء،\r\n\r\nنود اعلام حضراتكم بأنه اعتباراً من يوم الاحد الموافق 15/1 سنقوم بنشر \"موضوعات الدروس الاسبوعية\" معكم لكي تكونوا على علم بما يتعلمه اطفالكم.\r\n\r\nمع اطيب التحيات',	0,	'2023-01-10 10:06:07',	'2023-01-10 10:06:07',	NULL),
(371,	'The Termly Attendance Policy',	'Dear parents,\r\n\r\nPlease review the below policy:\r\n\r\nExcused absence:\r\n\r\n-Funeral: 2 days\r\n-Sick students: based on a doctor\'s note\r\n-Unfortunate circumstances: subject to management approval\r\n\r\n1 unexcused absence will result in a verbal warning\r\n2 unexcused absences will result in a written warning\r\n3 unexcused absences will result in an internal suspension for 1 day \r\n4 unexcused absences will result in an internal suspension for 2 days\r\n5 unexcused absences will result in an external suspension for 4 days \r\n6 unexcused absences: the student will not be able to be enrolled the following term\r\n\r\nThree late passes will be considered as an absence for a full day.\r\n\r\n Detention\r\n\r\nDetention (Behavioral Reasons) :\r\n3 detentions will result in an internal suspension\r\n4 detentions will result in an external suspension \r\n5 detentions could result for the student not to be enrolled the following term\r\n\r\n\r\n-Students who fail to do their homework will be sent to the detention room to do their homework\r\n\r\n-Students who speak Arabic outside of the Arabic class will be sent to detention too.\r\n\r\nRegards,',	0,	'2023-01-10 11:37:56',	'2023-01-10 11:37:56',	NULL),
(373,	'Homework for KGs/G1/G2',	'Dear parents,\r\n\r\nKindly note that if teachers assign homework, it is optional for children to complete it. We strongly encourage students to do private study at home. The school officially assigns homework for G3-G10 students.\r\n\r\nRegards, \r\n\r\nاولياء الامور الاعزاء،\r\n\r\nنود التنويه الى ان تعيين الواجبات المنزلية من قبل المعلمين هو امر اختياري لطلبة صفوف KGs/ G1/ G2. نحن نشجع الطلبة على مراجعة الدروس في المنزل. تقوم المدرسة بتعيين الواجبات للصفوف G3-G10.\r\n\r\nمع اطيب التحيات',	0,	'2023-01-12 09:39:48',	'2023-01-12 09:39:48',	NULL),
(374,	'G1 Weekly Lesson Objectives 15/01/2023',	'Dear Parent,\r\nYour child will be studying the following material this week:\r\n\r\nSubject	Lesson Objectives\r\nEnglish	 Story: Keeping A Pet & This Is My Pet!\r\n•	How to identify and make commands.\r\n•	How to write instructions.\r\n•	How to guess what will happen next.\r\n•	How to identify and think of nouns.\r\n•	How to use adjectives.\r\n•	How to make words plural.\r\n•	How to ask and answer questions.\r\n•	How to design a poster.\r\n•	Noun phrases.\r\n•	Tricky words.\r\nMath	•	Add and subtract multiples of 10.\r\n•	Position words.\r\n•	Length: centimeters, decimetres, meters. \r\nScience	•	Habitats: \r\n•	Extreme Habitats.\r\n•	Micro-habitats\r\n•	Contrasting Habitats.\r\n•	Minibeasts.\r\nIPC	Explore different holidays and celebrations.\r\nIntroduction into basic vocabulary related to holidays and celebrations.\r\nArabic	دراسة حرف م والتدرب على م مع حروف (ا-و-ي) والحركات القصيرة (فتحة-ضمة-كسرة-سكون) اضافة إلى التدريبات الصوتية الخاصة بالحرف ص 62\r\nتدريبات ص61 إلى ص 72\r\nقراءة ص66\r\nArt	 Learn how to do draw James Rizzi birds\r\nCitizenship	Understand how to recognize a mistake.\r\nLearn the importance of telling the truth.\r\nLearn how to admit mistakes and apologize.\r\n If you require any further clarification please feel free to reach out to our school.\r\n\r\n Regards, \r\n EISB Management',	17,	'2023-01-15 05:57:49',	'2023-01-15 05:57:49',	NULL),
(375,	'G2 Weekly Lesson Objectives 15/1/2023',	'Dear Parent,\r\nYour child will be studying the following material this week:\r\n\r\n\r\nEnglish\r\nUse commas to separate items in lists of nouns\r\nLearn about Quantifiers as determiners\r\nWrite sentences for a simple report\r\nUse labels in non-fiction texts\r\nPresent information\r\n\r\n\r\nMath\r\nDouble numbers to 50 using partitioning\r\nHalve even numbers to 100  using partitioning\r\n\r\nScience\r\nDiscover where light comes from\r\nExplore sources of light\r\nLearn about reflecting light\r\n\r\nIPC\r\n What different countries are like\r\n How the climate affects the way people live\r\n\r\nArabic\r\nقصة رسالة إلى الكون من ورشة القراءة ص64-65 & فكر وتفكر ت5 ص66\r\nهيا نحكي ص59\r\nورشة المفردات -ت1 ص61/ ت3 ص62/ ت4 ص63/ ورشة الكتابة ت1 ص 68\r\n\r\nArt\r\nLearn how to draw James Rizzi Skyscraper\r\n\r\nCitizenship\r\nConnecting with Nature : Take pleasure in being outdoors\r\n\r\n If you require any further clarification, please feel free to reach out to our school.\r\n\r\n Regards, \r\n EISB Management',	18,	'2023-01-15 06:01:01',	'2023-01-15 06:01:01',	NULL),
(376,	'G3 Weekly Lesson Objectives 15/1/2023',	'Dear Parent,\r\n\r\nYour child will be studying the following material this week:\r\n\r\nEnglish\r\n Read and understand a text (Real Life: Daredevils)\r\nExplore difference between biography and autobiography\r\nKnow difference between first person and third person\r\nClarify information and timelines in the text\r\nUse present and past tense form of irregular verbs in writing\r\nLook at differences between a book and PowerPoint\r\nUse correct grammar and punctuation in writing (capital letters, commas, periods)\r\n\r\n\r\nMath\r\n Place value of 3 and 4 digit numbers\r\nRounding up and down on a number line\r\nRounding to the nearest 10, 100 and 1000\r\nWord problems: addition/subtraction using place value\r\n\r\nScience\r\n Grouping living things\r\nSorting and classifying animals and plants\r\nIdentifying features of living classifications\r\n\r\nIPC\r\n Land, sea and sky\r\nDifference between plants and water plants\r\nStudy water habitats\r\n\r\nArabic\r\nورشة المفردات ت2 ص55 & ت4 ص56 ( الكلمات البصرية)\r\nورشة الكتابة ت2 ص 64\r\nقصة انا اسف من ورشة القراءة ص94 & فكر وتفكر  ت5 ص97\r\nالواجب البيتي : التدرب على قراءة كلمات ت2& ت4 من ورشة المفردات / حل ت 2 من ورشة الكتابة\r\n\r\nArt \r\nLearn how to draw James Rizzi Skyscraper\r\n\r\nCitizenship\r\n Conflicts in the community: Bullying\r\nKey vocabulary\r\nLearn how bullying affects people\r\nComplete text using correct words\r\nWriting-supporting a student being bullied\r\nDesign a poster supporting a person being bullied\r\n\r\n If you require any further clarification, please feel free to reach out to our school.\r\n\r\n Regards,\r\n EISB Management',	19,	'2023-01-15 06:03:41',	'2023-01-15 06:03:41',	NULL),
