(90,	'اجازة',	'Exams',	'received',	'السلام عليكم \nاود طلب اجازة للطالبين لانا وعبدًالله احسان علي گريد ٩ وً١٠ لهذا اليوم ويوم غدا واتمنى ان كان بوسعهم اخذ الامتحانات التجريبيةالمتبقية بعد عطلة الكرسمس\nمع التقدير',	409,	'2022-12-14 06:25:18',	'2022-12-14 06:33:07',	'عزيزي ولي الامر،\r\n\r\nوعليكم السلام ورحمة الله وبركاته\r\n\r\nالرجاء ذكر سبب الغياب . اذا كان السبب مرض الاولاد، يرجى تزويدنا بتقرير او وصفة طبية ليتسنى للطلبة اعادة الامتحانات الفصل القادم.\r\n\r\nشاكرين تعاونكم',	NULL),
(91,	'Mrs. Barbara',	'Other',	'received',	'After greetings .. Please look at the mothers’ requests for your approval to re-work by sending pictures and videos of the children during the school day (by returning the WhatsApp groups and making them designated for this purpose only) so that we can share with them even a small part of their long school day and so that we have them as a memory and like most of the schools do and as we were used to before from you, we ask for your approval.. With thanks and appreciation',	22,	'2022-12-14 06:49:45',	'2022-12-15 11:28:01',	'Dear Parents, \r\n\r\nThank you very much for your suggestion We will be posting pictures of students\' events and activities through the school application, \"Activities\" icon. Sorry for the inability of teachers to publish pictures because they are busy with the end of term 1 exams. \r\n\r\nThanks for your understanding',	NULL),
(92,	'إلى إدارة المدرسة الانكليزية',	'Other',	'received',	'بعد التحية .. يرجى النظر الى طلبات الامهات بموافقتكم على اعادة العمل بإرسال صور وفيدوهات الاطفال اثناء اليوم الدراسي (عن طريق ارجاع مجاميع الوتس اب وجعلها مخصصة لهذا الغرض فقط) ليتسنى لنا مشاركتهم ولو جزءً بسيطاً من يومهم الدراسي الطويل ولتبقى لدينا ذكرى وكما هو معمول في اغلب المدارس وكما عودتمونا سابقاً راجين موافقتكم .. مع الشكر والتقدير',	22,	'2022-12-14 06:51:31',	'2022-12-15 11:30:10',	'عزيزي ولي الامر،\r\n\r\nجزيل الشكر لمقترحكم \r\n\r\nسنقوم بنشر صور لفعاليات وانشطة الطلبة عن طريق تطبيق المدرسة من خلال ايقونة \"انشطة/activities\". المعذرة لعدم قدرة المعلمين على نشر الصور وذلك لانشغالهم بالامتحانات الفصلية.',	NULL),
(94,	'meeting with home teacher',	'Teacher',	'received',	'Meeting about mahdy status for grade 2',	127,	'2023-01-02 08:32:17',	'2023-01-02 12:18:15',	'Dear parent,\r\n\r\nThank you for submitting your request. \r\n\r\nKindly schedule a meeting with the teacher through \"Appointment\" and we will call you to provide you with date/time of the meeting.\r\n\r\nRegards,',	NULL),
(95,	'holiday',	'Other',	'received',	'school is open tomorrow?',	285,	'2023-01-02 16:45:00',	'2023-01-03 05:11:05',	'Dear parent,\r\n\r\nGood morning\r\n\r\nYes, school is open today.\r\n\r\nRegards,',	NULL),
(96,	'Changing class teachers',	'Teacher',	'received',	'Happy New Year to all of you in EISB!\n\nI would like to know if Mr. Smanga (G9) will ever come back as he was a very good teacher and moreover a very nice person and great mentor to the kids.\n\nas well, Me. Bores (G7) is another loss for the kids!\n\nappreciate your advice, and please put in consideration that those two teachers were perfect to their classes!\n\nThanks,',	325,	'2023-01-03 06:02:49',	'2023-01-03 08:58:37',	'Dear parent,\r\n\r\nWe truly appreciate your feedback\r\n\r\nUnfortunately, Mr Smanga is not coming back, and we are sad as well. We can assure you that G9 students will be happy with the new teacher \"Mr Danial\". \r\nIt is a matter of time, and we are positive that he is an excellent teacher. \r\n\r\nBest regards,',	NULL),
(97,	'Payment of fees',	'Accounting',	'received',	'could you please remind me the time for the next payment?',	285,	'2023-01-09 20:15:53',	'2023-01-11 05:56:01',	'Dear parent, \r\n\r\nThe term 1 and 2 tuition fees must be paid no later than January. Term 3 installment must be paid no later than March. \r\n\r\nIf you have not cleared your child’s tuition for term 1 and 2 , please visit the finance department by the end of this week. \r\n\r\nRegards,',	NULL),
(107,	'New schedule',	'Other',	'received',	'hello I would like to have the new schedule posted on the app or classroom',	426,	'2023-01-15 14:15:39',	'2023-01-17 05:34:34',	'Dear parent, we have posted yesterday the updated timetables for all grades.',	NULL),
(108,	'Pick up request',	'Other',	'received',	'Please note that today new person will pick up Farshid Saleh Ivo from Shcool. Mr. Azad vehicle no. 24/2 will pick up him.\nThe regular driver is away today.',	285,	'2023-01-17 09:57:00',	'2023-01-18 12:25:44',	'Dear parent,\r\n\r\nThank you for notifying us. Well received.\r\n\r\nRegards,',	NULL),
(109,	'ذو الفقار علي',	'Accounting',	'received',	'مرحبا متى تسليم النتاج للصف kc1',	10,	'2023-01-18 23:02:50',	'2023-01-19 04:41:11',	'عزيزي ولي الامر،\r\n\r\nاهلا وسهلا بحضرتكم\r\n\r\nسيتم توزيع النتائج الاسبوع القادم ان شاء الله.\r\n\r\nمع اطيب التحيات،',	NULL),
(110,	'Extra Math lesson',	'Teacher',	'received',	'Dears,\nI was promised that Ms. Shahad will support my daughter (Reem G7) with Math as she doesn’t understand well from the current teacher! please be informed that she hasn’t received any booster lesson yet\nappreciate your cooperation in this matter! thanks',	325,	'2023-01-22 22:16:31',	'2023-01-23 12:35:08',	'Greetings,\r\n\r\nThank you for informing us. I have checked that the student Reem Al Forati will be joining maths support lessons this week on Wednesday and Thursday. The reason of her joining this week and not the previous week is due to the fact that the teacher had to reschedule her timetable based on when the student\'s timetable. We apologize for the late response and hope that the student uprise in her maths studies.',	NULL),
(111,	'اجازة',	'Medical status',	'received',	'السلام عليكم \nاود طلب اجازة لبنتي لانا احسان علي گريد ١٠ بسبب طرف صحي.\nمع التقدير',	409,	'2023-01-23 12:27:48',	'2023-01-23 12:50:49',	'وعليكم السلام. نتمنتى للطالبة الشفاء العاجل. الرجاء ارسال صورة للتقرير الطبي عبر الواتساب او مع الطالبة  في حال رجوعها حتى تعتبر لها اجازة.  شاكرين تعاونكم معنا',	NULL),
(112,	'Science',	'Other',	'received',	'Dears, \nwould you please let me know if science book will be delivered to students, Reem haven’t received one yet\nThanks,',	325,	'2023-01-23 16:40:19',	'2023-01-24 10:42:58',	'Dear parent, \r\nThe science book will be given out to the students once its delivered. It is taking time because of the shipment process.  We will give the science book to the student (Reem Alforati G7) soon. We thank you for your patience.',	NULL),
(113,	'المنصور',	'Exams',	'received',	'يرجى ارسال المواضيع الداخله بل امتحان خلال اسبوع القادم يرسلوه باجر حتى نبدي ندرسهم ويتهيئون ونعرف شون نظام الاسئله حتكون',	142,	'2023-01-24 02:34:05',	'2023-01-24 14:35:09',	'عزيزي ولي الامرة،\r\n\r\nسيتم نشر مادة الامتحان غدا باذنه تعالى.\r\n\r\nمع اطيب التحيات،',	NULL),
